<meta property="og:title" content="Street Fighter 6 Character Comparison (Tier, CPV, T3R) | FGC Top Players">
<meta property="og:description" content="Compare up to 5 SF6 characters side-by-side with CPV (Competitive Performance Viability) and T3R Momentum. Save and share your presets.">
